title: 249: If We Could Witness Any Historical Event | Ear Biscuits Ep.249
description:
Who knew that diving deep into science, religion, and aliens would open a door to vulnerability and introspection? R&L each discuss 3 historical events that they would go back in time to witness and why in this episode of Ear Biscuits!
